OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776892266
OL,3,CBird flu jab trial starts amid 'real
OL,4,Cpossibility' of human-to-human
OL,5,Ctransmission
OL,7,FA first-of-its-kind trial has been
OL,8,Flaunched to test a new vaccine for
OL,9,Fbird flu in humans, amid the "real
OL,10,Fpossibility" of human-to-human
OL,11,Ftransmission.
OL,13,FThousands of people in the UK are
OL,14,Fexpected to be recruited for the
OL,15,Fstudy, with poultry farmers or those
OL,16,Fwho have close contact with birds
OL,17,Fencouraged to sign up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776892266
OL,3,CBird flu jab trial starts amid 'real
OL,4,Cpossibility' of human-to-human
OL,5,Ctransmission
OL,7,FExperts have warned that the A(H5N1)
OL,8,Fstrain of the virus is evolving and
OL,9,Fspreading in animals, and while it
OL,10,Fdoes not yet move easily between
OL,11,Fpeople, society must be wary of the
OL,12,Frisks of human-to-human transmission
OL,13,Fdeveloping.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776892266
OL,3,CBird flu jab trial starts amid 'real
OL,4,Cpossibility' of human-to-human
OL,5,Ctransmission
OL,7,FDr Rebecca Clark, who is based at
OL,8,FLayton Medical Centre in Blackpool and
OL,9,Fis the trial's national co-ordinating
OL,10,Finvestigator, said: "We know that the
OL,11,FA(H5N1) strain is evolving and
OL,12,Fspreading across animal species, and
OL,13,Fthough it does not yet move easily
OL,14,Fbetween humans, we have to treat human-
OL,15,Fto-human transmission as a real
OL,16,Fpossibility.
OL,18,F"This trial is our proactive attempt
OL,19,Fto shield against that possibility,
OL,20,Fand any future pandemic that could
OL,21,Femerge from it."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776892266
OL,3,CBird flu jab trial starts amid 'real
OL,4,Cpossibility' of human-to-human
OL,5,Ctransmission
OL,7,FThe mRNA-1018 vaccine, developed by
OL,8,FModerna, uses mRNA technology, similar
OL,9,Fto jabs for Covid-19.
OL,11,FIt instructs the body to produce
OL,12,Fspecific proteins from a specific
OL,13,Fvirus to help train the immune system
OL,14,Fto recognise and respond quickly if it
OL,15,Fcomes into contact with the illness.
OL,17,FThe phase 3 trial will include around
OL,18,F4,000 people in the UK and the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776892266
OL,3,CBird flu jab trial starts amid 'real
OL,4,Cpossibility' of human-to-human
OL,5,Ctransmission
OL,7,FSome 3,000 UK patients ` half of whom
OL,8,Fwill be over 65 ` will have the jabs
OL,9,Fat 26 sites across England and
OL,10,FScotland.
OL,12,FThe A(H5N1) strain has come to affect
OL,13,Fbirds globally in recent years, but
OL,14,Fhas also caused outbreaks among other
OL,15,Fanimals such as mink and marine
OL,16,Fmammals.
OL,18,FIt had also spread to dairy cows in
OL,19,Fthe US, with several human cases in
OL,20,Fthose working on farms with affected
OL,21,Fcattle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776892266
OL,3,CBird flu jab trial starts amid 'real
OL,4,Cpossibility' of human-to-human
OL,5,Ctransmission
OL,7,FThe study, backed by the National
OL,8,FInstitute for Health and Care Research
OL,9,F(NIHR) and sponsored by Moderna, will
OL,10,Ftake seven months, with patients given
OL,11,Ftwo doses of the vaccine three weeks
OL,12,Fapart.
OL,14,FAccording to Dr Hiwot Hiruy, senior
OL,15,Fdirector of clinical development at
OL,16,FModerna, said early trials of the jab
OL,17,Ffound it to be "generally well
OL,18,Ftolerated, with most of the side-
OL,19,Feffects being mild to moderate, and
OL,20,Fthere were no safety concerns".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776892266
OL,3,CBird flu jab trial starts amid 'real
OL,4,Cpossibility' of human-to-human
OL,5,Ctransmission
OL,7,FShe added: "We also saw that mRNA-1018
OL,8,Finduced a strong immune response, and
OL,9,Fthat we were able to pick that immune
OL,10,Fresponse as early as seven days after
OL,11,Fthe first injection, and the immune
OL,12,Fresponse persisted."
OL,14,FGiven the absence of bird flu in
OL,15,Fhumans, researchers will use the
OL,16,Fimmune response as an early indicator
OL,17,Fthat the treatment is likely to work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
