OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776892266
OL,3,CBird flu jab trial starts amid 'real
OL,4,Cpossibility' of human-to-human
OL,5,Ctransmission
OL,7,FThe A(H5N1) bird flu viruses first
OL,8,Femerged in southern China in 1996,
OL,9,Fwith the first human infections
OL,10,Frecorded a year later.
OL,12,FSince 2024, there have been 116
OL,13,Fconfirmed cases of bird flu in people
OL,14,Facross the world, with almost all
OL,15,Flinked to close contact with infected
OL,16,Fanimals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776892266
OL,3,CBird flu jab trial starts amid 'real
OL,4,Cpossibility' of human-to-human
OL,5,Ctransmission
OL,7,FDr Richard Pebody, director of
OL,8,Fepidemic and emerging infections at
OL,9,Fthe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA),
OL,10,Fsaid: "We clearly don't know when the
OL,11,Fnext pandemic is going to be, we
OL,12,Fobviously don't know what it's going
OL,13,Fto be caused by, but what we do know
OL,14,Fis that a flu pandemic is the most
OL,15,Flikely future pandemic."
OL,17,FHe added that while the current risk
OL,18,Fof bird flu in humans "remains low"
OL,19,Fthe virus "continues to evolve".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
