OL,3,CBird flu jab trial starts amid 'real
OL,4,Cpossibility' of human-to-human
OL,5,Ctransmission
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,F"UKHSA remains alert to the potential
OL,13,Fthat this pathogen could adapt to
OL,14,Fspread from person to person, and will
OL,15,Fcontinue to monitor all available
OL,16,Fdata," Dr Pebody said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
