OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776892266
OL,3,CBird flu jab trial starts amid 'real
OL,4,Cpossibility' of human-to-human
OL,5,Ctransmission
OL,7,FAt the end of 2024, the government
OL,8,Fannounced it had agreed a contract for
OL,9,Fmore than five million doses of an H5
OL,10,Finfluenza vaccine to bolster pandemic
OL,11,Fpreparedness.
OL,13,FThe jab is based on a current H5 bird
OL,14,Fflu virus.
OL,16,FHowever, Dr Pebody said that the
OL,17,Fcurrent stockpile uses more
OL,18,Ftraditional vaccine technology.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776892266
OL,3,CBird flu jab trial starts amid 'real
OL,4,Cpossibility' of human-to-human
OL,5,Ctransmission
OL,7,FDr Hiruy also said that mRNA vaccines
OL,8,Fcan be produced faster and can be
OL,9,Fadjusted to strains rapidly.
OL,11,FShe said that while there are other
OL,12,Fvaccines out there, the new jab would
OL,13,Fbe an "additional tool in pandemic
OL,14,Fpreparedness"".
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
